        {
          "question": "<p>Match the items in column I with one or more items of column II :</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Column I</strong></td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Column II</strong></td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(i) Upper jaw</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(a) have fins on the body</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(ii)&nbsp;Fish</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(b) has an outer skeleton</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(iii) Ribs</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(c) can fly in the air</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(iv) Snail</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(d) is an immovable joint</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(v)&nbsp;Cockroach</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(e) protect the heart</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>",
          "id": 92348,
          "options_data": [],
          "solution_data": [
            {
              "id": 33793,
              "solution": "<p>The correct order of the match is&nbsp;(i)-(d),&nbsp;(ii)-(a),&nbsp;(iii)-(e),&nbsp;(iv)-(b), and&nbsp;(v)-(c).</p>"
